import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

fig, ax = plt.subplots()
sns.scatterplot(data=penguins,
                x="bill_length_mm",
                y="flipper_length_mm",
                hue="species",
                ax=ax)
ax.set_title("Penguins: Bill vs Flipper Length")
